    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep your sporting goods and fitness equipment handy with the Jumbo Aluminum Carabiner! The Jumbo Carabiner is a great item to bring along camping, hiking, to the gym and just about any outdoor activity. Attach one to your backpack, water bottle, keys or purse to keep things handy and organized. These carabiners are constructed of durable aluminum and feature a soft cushion grip for added comfort. They come in 6 colors: black, silver, red, green, blue and pink. The jumbo carabiners also make a great handle for dog-walking! Attach it to your favorite leash and you&#039;ll have a sturdy, comfortable handle. Make sure to grab a few of these to keep around the house, your office or outdoor gear! Please note: these carabiners are NOT FOR CLIMBING.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">7 Inch Jumbo Aluminum Carabiner Hiking Cushion Grip (6 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Keep your sporting goods and fitness equipment handy with the Jumbo Aluminum Carabiner!</p>\n  <p>The Jumbo Carabiner is a great item to bring along camping, hiking, to the gym and just about any outdoor activity. Attach one to your backpack, water bottle, keys or purse to keep things handy and organized.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 6.5&quot; x 4&q